  "text": "All MD simulations were performed using the AMBER10 program [26] with 2 fs time step size. The long range electrostatic interactions were treated by using the particle mesh of Ewald's method [CITATION_1] with a 10.0 Å cut-off distance. The SHAKE algorithm [CITATION_2] was applied to constrain the bonds involving hydrogen atoms.",
